│ Pending tasks:      ██░░░░░░░░ 2/15            │
│ Timeout:            45s remaining              │
│                                                │
│ Resources:                                     │
│   ✓ Database pool closed                       │
│   ◐ Redis connections draining                 │
│   ○ File handles (pending)                     │
│                                                │
